    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p>\r\n<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a matching lid&nbsp;over a medium heat</p>\r\n<p>Meanwhile, chop the&nbsp;<strong>asparagus&nbsp;</strong>in half (chop them in one bunch for speed!)</p>",
