    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the&nbsp;<strong>asparagus&nbsp;</strong>to the pan with a pinch of&nbsp;<strong>salt&nbsp;</strong>and a small splash of&nbsp;<strong>cold&nbsp;water&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Cover and cook for 3-4 min or until bright green and tender with a slight bite</p>\r\n<p>Once done, remove the pan from the heat and set aside until serving</p>",
